753
00:38:20,117 --> 00:38:21,020
Scott: It is an old problem.

754
00:38:21,380 --> 00:38:26,659
Rym: But you know how you watch 1776, for example, and they keep like, "I move to do

755
00:38:26,699 --> 00:38:26,880
