768
00:39:50,461 --> 00:40:06,120
Rym: One person will take all the ire, but at the same time, that person is very unpersonable and impassive and impersonal, and as a result, you can diffuse the drama that would occur when people don't get their way because the system did it, no individual person did it.

769
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:11,180
Rym: That is the greatest contribution Robert's Rules of Order will bring.

770
00:40:11,840 --> 00:40:14,100
